    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/43882b753cd0725fa58bf5d0b254aef4.poster.avif?t=1757954150\" width=1154 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/43882b753cd0725fa58bf5d0b254aef4.webm?t=1757954150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/43882b753cd0725fa58bf5d0b254aef4.mp4?t=1757954150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>NOWGUN</strong> 是一款基于格子战斗的 roguelite 竞技场游戏，生存不仅仅依靠战斗，还取决于你如何利用有限的移动。以下是你需要知道的游戏内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/c094db2a6c07e59d6b7ee45540938495.poster.avif?t=1757954150\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/c094db2a6c07e59d6b7ee45540938495.webm?t=1757954150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/c094db2a6c07e59d6b7ee45540938495.mp4?t=1757954150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关卡不仅仅是战斗：</strong> 要通过每一关，你只需要用完所有的移动。是的，你可以通过逃避敌人来生存一段时间，但你不会在后来的关卡中走得太远！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对敌人还是逃跑？</strong> 虽然逃跑可以让你活得久一些，但最终你需要面对敌人并变得更强。随着深入，敌人会变得更强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>两种攻击方式：</strong> 你有两种攻击敌人的方式——远程或近战。每次攻击发生在你或敌人移动之后。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>远程攻击消耗移动：</strong> 远程攻击需要你改变位置，这会消耗宝贵的移动。你越高效，越能在一波中击败更多敌人。效率至关重要！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一关都会变强：</strong> 每一关结束后，你会解锁与跳过的关卡数相等的宝箱。里面有强力道具，可以让你变得更强，为接下来的战斗做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/68f0a6bf7245d8856aabc9c1207e59c9.poster.avif?t=1757954150\" width=1014 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/68f0a6bf7245d8856aabc9c1207e59c9.webm?t=1757954150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165800/extras/68f0a6bf7245d8856aabc9c1207e59c9.mp4?t=1757954150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>额外掉落：</strong> 击败敌人可能掉落包含额外属性的宝箱，让你在前进过程中变得更强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>终极目标：</strong> 推动自己看看你能走多远，面对越来越强的敌人，能坚持多久？</p>",
